# xAI API Configuration
API_URL=https://api.x.ai/v1/chat/completions
MODEL_NAME=grok-3-fast-latest
TEMPERATURE=0

# Server Configuration (for local development only)
# PORT and HOST will be automatically set by Render in production
PORT=10000
HOST=0.0.0.0
DEBUG=false

# Security
SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key-change-this-in-production

# Python Configuration
PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1
PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE=1

# Usage Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp env.example .env
# 2. Edit .env and set your actual values
# 3. Never commit .env to version control
# 4. For Render deployment, set environment variables in Render dashboard
# 5. PORT and HOST are automatically managed by Render
# 6. MODEL_NAME supports: grok-3-fast-latest, grok-3-beta, grok-3-fast
# 7. TEMPERATURE: Model temperature (0-1, default: 0)
# 8. DEBUG: Enable debug mode (true/false, default: false)
# 9. SECRET_KEY: Flask secret key (auto-generated in Render)

# Notes:
# 1. Copy this file to .env and fill in your configuration
# 2. You need a valid xAI API key to use Live Search functionality
# 3. Live Search is currently in free public beta (until June 5, 2025)
# 4. In production, use a strong SECRET_KEY
# 5. Render will automatically set PORT and HOST variables

# 注意：
# 1. 复制此文件为 .env 并填入您的配置
# 2. 您需要有效的 xAI API 密钥才能使用 Live Search 功能
# 3. Live Search 功能目前处于免费公开测试阶段（截止到2025年6月5日）
# 4. 在生产环境中，请设置强密码作为 SECRET_KEY
# 5. MODEL_NAME 支持: grok-3-fast-latest, grok-3-beta, grok-3-fast 